{"tid":665033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【石棺藏屍】梁振英亦列懸紅名單 價值100萬美金","createTime":"2018-05-14T14:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T16:10:22.000Z","uid":160807,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1f25cbfcc2d86af267263399bddce45280cf13","tid":665033,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180514/rphoto/1526275049_9ee7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180514%2Frphoto%2F1526275049_9ee7.png&h=8e9fe4c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣DAN6大廈石棺藏屍案今續審，首被告曾祥欣（阿T）續接受第三被告大狀盤問，<span style=\"color: red;\">期間透露前特首梁振英亦在「There」懸紅名單上，惟他只價值100萬美金</span>；阿T另承認曾在「There」會議上吹噓在外太空擁有一個衛星系統，而「There」的所有通訊均由衛星控制。<span style=\"color: red;\">大狀指阿T曾在會議上揚言要炸毀本港3條海底隧道</span>、又吹噓可控制一枚原子彈的發射系統，阿T回應曾有人提及，但否認是他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526272122_140e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526272122_140e.jpg&h=0398d9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首被告曾祥欣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526272123_dd67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526272123_dd67.jpg&h=0aea7a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前特首梁振英<br />\n<br />\n代表第三被告的大狀徐福亮續盤問阿T，要求阿T逐一翻閱其警誡會面謄本。法官李瀚良指出，阿T在首次警誡中指次被告劉錫豪（阿豪）用手掩住死者張萬里（阿J）的鼻、後來卻改口指是掩住阿J的口，問到底哪一個答案才是正確，阿T指「佢（阿豪）行開咗，我見到塊毛巾遮住咗成個樣，所以佢又掩住口又掩住鼻，你話口又得、鼻又得。」阿T在追問下承認沒親眼看見阿豪當時到底是掩住阿J的口還是鼻、抑或是兩者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大狀問阿T，是否曾經在「There」會議中提及如果殺死前特首梁振英則可獲100萬美金，阿T否認指「我冇講過殺，我講緊佢嘅價值。</span>大狀問梁振英是否在他們所幻想的「Delete Record（刪除記錄）」名單上，阿T同意。大狀問阿T曾否在會議中揚言炸毀本港3條海底隧道、又自吹自擂在外太空擁有一個衛星系統、並可控制一枚原子彈的發射系統，阿T承認曾吹噓擁有衛星系統；至於另外兩者，他澄清是其他人提及的，並非他。阿T強調在會議中所提及的事只屬「吹水」，是一班朋友在飲醉酒下的幻想，根本沒有人認真看待，況且「根本做唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n阿T曾在警誡中向警方指，案發當日因發現家中個哥羅芳即將用完，於是外出購買，李官問他「你成日係屋企用哥羅芳？」阿T回應「我屋企樓梯架下面，全部都用哥羅芳痴」，李官不明所以，阿T解釋「亞加力膠的書架」；李官疑惑問即用哥羅芳黏貼亞加力書架？阿T承認，並謂售賣膠片的老闆向他揚言可用哥羅芳黏貼膠架。李官笑問他家中有很多亞加力書架需要黏貼嗎？阿T指碰巧有人表示哥羅芳可以弄暈人，又有人謂打算在當天弄暈阿J，他於是便外出購買。惟當被問「有人」即是誰，阿T表示當日他們三名被告一同開會，但不記得是誰提出的。<br />\n3名被告曾祥欣（27歲）、劉錫豪（22歲）及張善恒（24歲）被控於2016年3月4日謀殺男子張萬里（28歲）。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6790d29f9a6d15a0bfd4c3f414239d6da954e1ab","tid":665033,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"補返條link: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180514/58190449?_ga=2.11261490.785510576.1525752234-2070346420.1524966476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F58190449%3F_ga%3D2.11261490.785510576.1525752234-2070346420.1524966476&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4917dce4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F58190449%3F_ga%3D2.11261490.785510576.1525752234-2070346420.1524966476&h=dacea64e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180514/58190449?_ga=2.11261490.785510576.1525752234-2070346420.1524966476</a>"},{"pid":"eb366ffe4852b521da884fc13934c2461fe2e9f6","tid":665033,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"一班戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f04ba9b3658223c6118ef77be07d29c8009bc38","tid":665033,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"我睇緊乜撚嘢？"},{"pid":"a97e6647acced3609a9d5b8acb7441cda5e87e4a","tid":665033,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaad3590f749eadc0d0edd59def6c1ebfe8d591","tid":665033,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaaaa6b09c3fcf50248ef9e8e6653d0acf7775c","tid":665033,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beaad3590f749eadc0d0edd59def6c1ebfe8d591","tid":665033,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hk-pub.com/forum/aattachments/day_080103/20080103_f98d67f991bb6ccee8b2fOAF1nnIkEHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-pub.com%2Fforum%2Faattachments%2Fday_080103%2F20080103_f98d67f991bb6ccee8b2fOAF1nnIkEHu.jpg&h=21719f83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57bfebb3642bbd676d7c49c7d38ba44e3e365fea","tid":665033,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"呃人的最高境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}